items.title: A Soviet probe orbiting Earth since 1972 will soon reenter the planet's atmosphere
items.description: Kosmos 482 has been orbiting the Earth for decades. It's still unknown if the craft will fall to Earth intact or burn up upon atmospheric reentry.

items.title: Tourist boats capsize in sudden storm in southwest China, leaving 10 dead
items.description: More than 80 people fell into a river when strong winds hit the scenic area in Guizhou province late Sunday afternoon, state broadcaster CCTV said.
